Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I thought you were dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可你在干什么 "旅行"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and where were you? "Travelling"!
