Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想打电话来着 真的 我只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I meant to phone, I really did. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了 -忘了一年吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I forgot. - For a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我留在家一整年都想不起来打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You forgot for a year, and I'm left sitting here? !
