Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底怎么回事 就因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then what is it? Because you.
