Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是四十五岁 你是从网上钓到她的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}45? What, did you find her on the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在网上假装什么博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}go online and pretend you're a Doctor.
