Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,尝尝这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stitch this, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想过我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you think about me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想过 一直都想 只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did, all the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕一通电话 让我知道你还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}One phone call. Just to know that you were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 真的对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry, I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但更让我害怕的是你还不肯说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But d'you know, what terrifies me is that you still can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底发生了什么事 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What happened to you, Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么事糟到你都不能和我说的地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What can be so bad that you can't tell me, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能告诉她 我都不知道从何说起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't tell her. I can't even begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她永远都不会原谅我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's never going to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我失去了一年的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I missed a year.
