Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说九百年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}When you say 900 years. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的年纪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你九百岁了 -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're 900 years old. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈说得对 我们的代沟是有点大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My mum was right. That is one hell of an age gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,每次和你说话都变得这么疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Every conversation with you just goes mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可我又没别人可以倾诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's no-one else I can talk to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的那么多东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've seen all that stuff up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,见识了宇宙之广袤 却一个字都不能说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the size of it, and I can't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,外星人还有太空飞船还有那些…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Aliens and spaceships and things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是地球上唯一一个知道他们存在的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and I'm the only person on planet Earth who knows they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, that's just not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒霉催的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ah, just my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请后退 后退 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stay back, please. Back, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,已经封锁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's blocked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离中心还有好远呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're miles from the centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,全城肯定都堵住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The city must be gridlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,整个伦敦恐怕都要关停了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The whole of London must be closing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 真不敢相信我正好碰到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know! I can't believe I'm here to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太奇妙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就知道这会发生吗 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you know this was gonna happen? -Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那艘船吗 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you recognise the ship? - Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它为什么会坠毁吗 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you know why it crashed? - Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有你在真好 -我觉得也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So glad I've got you. - I bet you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我到处旅行的原因 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is why I travel for, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,历史就在我们眼前发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}History happening right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去看看啊 不用管交通情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, let's go and see it. Never mind the traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有塔迪斯 -最好不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}we've got the TARDIS. - Hmm. Better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有一艘太空飞船在伦敦中央\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}With one spaceship in the middle of London,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想再加一艘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't wanna shove another on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但是你的看起来像个蓝色大盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah. . .but yours looks like a big blue box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会注意到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No-one's gonna notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不一定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的情况出现时 各色人等都会盯着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Emergency like this, there will be all kinds of people watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 塔迪斯需要留在原地\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Trust me, the TARDIS stays where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以历史大事发生 我们却困在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So history is happening, and we're stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, we are. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,又是肯·利文斯通搞的鬼 对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This has gotta be Ken Livingstone, isn't...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以和大家一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We could do what everyone else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去看电视\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Watch it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦\N大本钟被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一架飞碟坠落于伦敦中央导致大本钟被毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Big Ben destroyed as a UFO crash-lands in central London.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦\N警方尽力控制围观者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,政府已从全国调集警力增援\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Police reinforcements are drafted in from across the country
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,控制大规模恐慌 劫掠和市民骚动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}to control widespread panic, looting and civil disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,并发布了全国紧急通报\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A state of national emergency has been declared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆·海金森从现场发回报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tom Hitchinson is at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,警方呼吁公众不要惊慌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The police urge the public not to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}外星人应急响应及求助热线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你担心家人或朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here's the helpline number on screen right now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请拨打屏幕下方的求助热线\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}if you're worried about friends or family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,军方正在监控是否有更多太空飞船的出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The military are on the lookout for more spaceships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,得到进一步确认之前 北美所有机场的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Until then all flights in North American airspace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机均已禁飞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}have been grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦\N军方潜水员在泰晤士河中寻找尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,军方向飞碟坠毁现场派出了潜水员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The army are sending divers into the wreck of the space ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道他们会发现什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}no-one knows what they're going to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,总统将在白宫向全国发表电视直播讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The President will address the nation live from the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但联合国秘书长已经呼吁大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but the Secretary General has asked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,时刻注意天空出现的异常情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that people watch the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我别无选择 -你伤了你妈妈的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've got no choice! - You broke your mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎他或者落得个再也见不到你的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Make him welcome or risk never seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还得我像哄孩子一样哄她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I cradled her like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我在听新闻呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi! I'm trying to listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦 首相府尚未发表评论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚得到消息…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}News just coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们把镜头转给正在河边的汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and we go to Tom at the embankment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦\N军方潜水员在泰晤士河中找到尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找到了一具尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They've found a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,目前还尚未证实\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's unconfirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但据传在失事地点找到了一具尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but I'm being told a body's been found in the wreckage,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一具非地球生物的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}a body of non-terrestrial origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它已经被带上岸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's being brought ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,太空飞船的废墟中疑似发现了一具尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A body of some sort has been found inside the wreckage of a spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,猜猜谁约我出去了 比利·克鲁特\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Guess who asked me out? Billy Croot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,未经证实的报道称\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Unconfirmed reports say
