Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,该尸体确实来自外星\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the body IS of extra-terrestrial origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦中心正在发生一起重大事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}An extraordinary event unfolding here live in central London.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体已被转移到一处重兵把守的停尸房\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The body is being transferred to a secure-unit mortuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,具体位置目前尚不清楚 道路…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}whereabouts as yet unknown. Roads in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦 武装警察在伦敦街头巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你贴机翼的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And when you've stuck your fins on
