Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧啊 用你喜欢的颜色上好糖霜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ooh look at that! Then, ice it any colour you want.
