Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦\N太空飞船中的尸体被送入医院看管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔比恩医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Albion Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还不知道它是死是活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We still don't know if it's alive or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,白厅否认一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Whitehall's denying everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但尸体已经被带到了阿尔比恩医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But the body has been brought here, Albion Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,由于道路拥堵 这是离河最近的医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}With roads closed, it's the closest to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我得知现在艾斯奎斯将军正在进入医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm being told that's General Asquith now entering the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大楼里的人已被疏散\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The building has been evacuated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其他病人也已经转移到了街上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}patients moved out onto the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,警方仍未确认在这大楼里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The police still won't confirm the presence of an alien body
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有外星人的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}contained inside those walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let's have a look, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And that's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是骗局或假人什么的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not a hoax or a dummy, or... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我对颅骨进行了X光扫描\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've X-rayed the skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的结构我从未见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's wired up inside like nothing I've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能造假到这种水平\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No one could make this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大批专家正在赶来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We've got experts being flown in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们来之前 把这东西藏好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Until they arrive, get that out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道现在是紧急状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know it's a state of emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且流言满天飞 但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and there's a lot of rumour flying around, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说的是真的吗 关于首相的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}is it true what they're saying? About the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,首相的去向依然迷雾重重\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mystery still surrounds the whereabouts of the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,自从紧急状态开始后就没人见过他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not been seen since the emergency began.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,反对党正在大肆批评他缺乏领导能力及…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The opposition are criticising his lack of leadership and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是约瑟夫·格林 哈特利戴尔的国会议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, that's Joseph Green, MP for Hartleydale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他是国会下院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's Chairman of the Parliamentary Commission
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,监控出口甜食含糖标准委员会主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}on the Monitoring of Sugar Standards in Exported Confectionery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 眼下最要紧的人物可不是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}With respect, hardly the most important person right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,英德拉·加奈什 先生 国防部初级秘书\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Indra Ganesh, sir, Junior Secretary with the MOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我将是您的联系人 -他到底在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll be your liaison. - Where the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能单独谈谈吗 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If we could talk in private, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我上楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Follow me upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哈丽特·琼斯 弗莱德尔北区议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Harriet Jones, MP for Flydale North.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 不能等等吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry, can't it wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的确预约了三点一刻和首相见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But I did have an appointment at 3:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对 可一架飞船刚在伦敦中心坠毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes. Then a spaceship crashed in the middle of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想您的安排可能得拖一拖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think the schedule might have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,您听说那外星人尸体的事了吗 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've heard about the alien body, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别说那个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里 首相在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where is he? Where's the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道 他人间蒸发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No one knows, he's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我得通知您\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have to inform you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,由于全城一片混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}with the city gridlocked
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,全体内阁成员又都被堵在伦敦城外\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and the Cabinet stranded outside London,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在您成了代理首相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that makes you become Acting Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就任\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}With the immediate effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, Lord! Oh, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我的胃有点紧张 那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pardon me. I-it's a nervous stomach. Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特·布莱恩 军情五处的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Margaret Blaine, she's with MI5.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没有更多信息了 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's no more information, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲自护送首相从内阁会议室上了专车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I personally escorted the PM from the Cabinet Room to his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是奥利弗·查尔斯 交通联络官\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is Oliver Charles, Transport Liaison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,车消失了 没有任何记录 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The car's disappeared. There's no record of it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是人间蒸发了 -我们先进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Literally vanished. - Right. Inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 这是应急条例\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Er, sir...emergency protocols,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,详述外星人入侵时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}detailing actions to be taken
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,英国政府应该采取的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}by the Government of the Great Britain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,相应行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}in the event of an alien incursion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妈呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Blimey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,该工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get to work, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And where'd you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说那里面人气太旺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's...just a bit human in there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,历史性的事件刚刚发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}History just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们在讨论哪里买得到半价的假充值卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're talking about where you can buy dodgy top-up cards half-price.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是出来走走而已 没别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm only off on a wander, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对 泰晤士河上漂着一架飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right. A spaceship on the Thames,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而你只是在闲逛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and you're just wandering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我根本无关 反正不是外星人入侵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nothing to do with me! It's not an invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的只是着陆时坠毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That was a genuine crash-landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下降角度 烟雾颜色 所有迹象都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Angle of descent, colour of smoke, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无作假痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也许这就是第一类接触呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So maybe this is it, first contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类与外星人间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The day mankind officially
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,首次正式联系上的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}comes into contact with an alien race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会插手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm not interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们得自己处理这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Cos you've got to handle this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这样 人类文明才算真正成熟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's when the human race finally grows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在今天早上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还是渺小脆弱的生物呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you were all tiny and small and made of clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你们踏出第一步了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now you can expand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不需要我 去欢庆历史性的一天吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't need me. Go and celebrate history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和你妈妈共度美好时光吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Spend time with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要保证你不会丢下我走掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Promise you won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这么着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,塔迪斯的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}TARDIS key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候给你一把了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}About time you have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}外星人着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,帅哥 快回来一起开派对啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi, gorgeous, come back and join the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}欢迎来到我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你好 外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还没人给你捎杯咖啡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet no one's brought you a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 -不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank you. - Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是不能进\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You still can't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 我的妙计被你看穿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Damn, you've seen through my cunning plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 但这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look, I'm sorry, it's just impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,两分钟都不行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not even for two minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里的机会并不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't get many chances to walk these corridors,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是"宝贝" 只是个忠诚的后座议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm hardly one of the "Babes", just a faithful backbencher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1\bord0}{\an9}指"布莱尔宝贝" 即1997年工党大选获胜的一百余位女议员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道现在新世界的大门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I know we've had a brave new world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,正在向我们敞开 这实在是太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}land right on our doorstep, and that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 这可能很棒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think that's...probably wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 平淡无奇的生活还要继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nevertheless, ordinary life keeps ticking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要递交这文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I need to enter this paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,格林先生 我知道您很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, Mr Green, sir, I know you're busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但您能否将这个纳入下次内阁会议的议程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but could you put this on the next Cabinet agenda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 -关于乡村医院的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is it? - Cottage hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我研究出了一种系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've worked out a system
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样乡村医院就不必与\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}where cottage hospitals need not be excluded
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,高等医院分离开来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}from Centres of Excellence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲正住在弗莱德尔养老院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You see, my mother's in the Flydale Infirmary,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的选区\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that's my constituency,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是个小地方 你可能不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}tiny little place, you wouldn't know it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但这让我有机会 -看在老天的份上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but it gives me a chance to... - By all the saints,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看清楚点好吗 大姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}get some perspective, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我忙着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}紧急条例 绝密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,启用Δ防御计划 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Defence Plan Delta! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,出动 出动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它是活的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,分头行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Spread out,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,通知外面 立即全面封锁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}tell the perimeter it's a lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐它还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God it's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,米克 特里 马上去侧间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mick! Terry! Side rooms! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,继续搜索 -安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Keep it moving! - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓 它原来是死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I swear, it was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,昏迷 休克 休眠 都有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Coma, shock, hibernation, anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,它是什么样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:22:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,它还在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.73,0:23:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它被吓着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,它很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.42,0:24:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫直接把电话打到我这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have the White House phoning me direct
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为唐宁街不接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}because Downing Street won't answer their calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.63,0:24:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太离谱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都还没开始进行疫苗项目呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We haven't even started the vaccination programme.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真是让人震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is appalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所有国家都在关注英国\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The nations of the world are watching the United Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一点小乱子而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, it has all been a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是现代历史上最大的危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's the greatest crisis in modern history,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.43,0:24:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而您什么都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and you've done nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.82,0:24:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,您的行为真是可耻 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your behaviour has been shameful, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在此坐镇的本该是您\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're supposed to be in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.15,0:24:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要积极正确的领导\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We need positive leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.04,0:24:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,整个首都都瘫痪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The capital's ground to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们只能假设\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Furthermore, we can only assume
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.86,0:24:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,首相的失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the Prime Minister's disappearance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.55,0:24:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是因外星人的某些敌对行为而造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}is the direct result of hostile alien action,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而您做了什么呢 什么都没做 -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and what've you been doing? Nothing! - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.10,0:24:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我想我现在就是首相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sorry, I thought I was Prime Minister now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.81,0:24:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在相位空缺的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Only by default!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.46,0:24:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh-h-h, that's not fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.30,0:25:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我可正乐在其中呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've been having such fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.43,0:25:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉着这好玩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You think this is fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.32,0:25:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这工作太逗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a hoot, this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.36,0:25:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 太欢乐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Honestly, it's super!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.39,0:25:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.82,0:25:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.91,0:25:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其他内阁成员在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where's the rest of the Cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么没坐飞机过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why haven't they been airlifted in?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我取消了行程 反正他们只会碍手碍脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I cancelled it. They'd get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.01,0:25:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我又来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oops, there I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.58,0:25:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.90,0:25:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我在扭屁屁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm...shaking my booty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.96,0:25:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 根据紧急条例第五章\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sir! Under Section 5 of the Emergency Protocols,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.55,0:25:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权解除你的指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it is my duty to relieve you of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.11,0:25:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果必要 我甚至可以对全国实施军事管制\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And by God, I'll put this country under martial law if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害怕呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ooh I'm scared
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.18,0:25:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.42,0:25:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,简直吓死我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that's hair-raising.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.64,0:25:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.52,0:25:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.25,0:26:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为外星人就长那个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I just assumed that's what aliens looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.11,0:26:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你却说它就是一只普通的地球猪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're saying it's an ordinary pig, from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.99,0:26:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就像美人鱼一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}More like a mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.79,0:26:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,维多利亚时期的马戏团经常把猫的骷髅\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Victorian showmen used to draw the crowds by
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.20,0:26:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和鱼尾粘在一起 称其为美人鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}taking the skull of a cat gluing into a fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.44,0:26:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,以此来吸引观众的眼球\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}then calling it a mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.48,0:26:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有人拿一只猪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now someone's taken a pig,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.08,0:26:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,改造了它的大脑 再重新粘合起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}opened up its brain, stuck bits on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,之后把它绑在那艘飞船里 使其坠毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then they strapped it in that ship, made it dive-bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:26:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它一定吓坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it must've been terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.58,0:27:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿这动物开了一个天大的玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They've taken this animal and turned it into a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.81,0:27:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这是假的 是仿造的 像美人鱼一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So it's a fake, a pretend, like the mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.28,0:27:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们用来扩容它大脑的技术\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But the technology augmenting its brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.94,0:27:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,却是地球上前所未见的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it's like nothing on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是外星技术 外星人假造外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's alien. Aliens are faking aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.26,0:27:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.26,0:27:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.94,0:27:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.50,0:27:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这杯敬那些火星人 -敬火星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here's to the Martians! - The Martians!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.60,0:27:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我正打算找你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was gonna come and see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.40,0:27:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,某些人还没跟米奇道歉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Someone owes Mickey an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.24,0:27:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 -不是说你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry. - Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.35,0:27:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,又不能怨我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, it's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.57,0:27:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,凭心而论 我还能怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Be fair, what was I supposed to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.85,0:28:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不见了 人们还会怀疑谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You disappear, who do they turn to?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是你男朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.46,0:28:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我被传讯了整整五次 五次啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Five times I was taken in for questioning. Five times!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.09,0:28:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有证据 怎么可能有 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No evidence. Of course, there couldn't be, could there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.33,0:28:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还有她 你妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And her, your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.27,0:28:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在邻居之间四处传播流言 对我指指点点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Whispering round the estate, pointing the finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.38,0:28:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还在我邮箱里塞那些乱七八糟的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stuff through my letterbox
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}all cos of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.57,0:28:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到我会离开这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I didn't think I'd be gone so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.15,0:28:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在等你 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And I waited for you, Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.03,0:28:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,整整12个月 我都在等你和博士回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}12 months, waiting for you and the Doctor to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.00,0:28:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着 你认识那个博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold on. You knew about the Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.95,0:28:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.35,0:28:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 为什么不说 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah, why not, Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.17,0:28:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我怎么告诉她你去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How could I tell her where you went?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.72,0:28:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tell me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.72,0:28:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是打算说 因为你现在哪也去不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I might as well, cos you're stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,博士已经走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The doctor's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.02,0:28:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就在刚才 那个盒子消失不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just now, that box thing just faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.31,0:28:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么 -他不要你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What d'you mean? - He's left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.43,0:28:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是这种男朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Some boyfriend he turned out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.23,0:28:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会就这么走了的 他答应过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He wouldn't just go. He promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.49,0:28:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他把你甩了 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Aw, he's dumped you, Rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人回到太空去了 你现在是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}sailed off into space. How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你和我们这些地球人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now you are left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.80,0:28:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,被扔在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}with the rest of us Earthlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.13,0:28:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢习惯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.04,0:28:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,按说他会跟我说一声的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But he would've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.17,0:29:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个究竟在说什么 到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are you two chimps going on about? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.09,0:29:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这个博士究竟怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's this Doctor done now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.46,0:29:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 他跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Huh! He's vamoosed!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.37,0:29:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有 他把这个留给了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not! Cos he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.02,0:29:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是我男朋友 米奇 他没那么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not my boyfriend, Mickey, he's better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.50,0:29:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他比这重要的多 他…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's much more important. And he. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.56,0:29:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈 你先回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mum! Mum! Go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.16,0:29:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别站在这儿 你先回去 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't stand there! Go inside, Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.29,0:29:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这究竟是怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How'd you do that, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.85,0:29:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我骗了你 我去看了一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}OK, so I lied. I went for a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.90,0:29:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,整个坠毁事件都是个阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The whole crash-landing's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.19,0:29:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是 简直太巧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I thought so - just too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.66,0:29:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然撞大本钟 得了吧 所以我就想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, hitting Big Ben, come on! So I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.00,0:29:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们去看看那个飞行员 -我妈妈来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}"let's go and have a look at the pilot." - My mum's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.88,0:29:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是如我所愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, just what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.95,0:30:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你休想把这里变成你家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't you dare make this place domestic!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.26,0:30:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你毁了我的生活 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You ruined my life, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.89,0:30:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都以为她死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They thought she was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.65,0:30:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你 我成了杀人嫌疑犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was a murder suspect because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.53,0:30:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我说什么来着 当自己家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You see what I mean? Domestic!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.58,0:30:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌 你甚至都不记得我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet you don't even remember my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.26,0:30:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.96,0:30:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是米奇 -不 是里奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's Mickey. - No, it's Ricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.44,0:30:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我知道自己叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think I know my own name!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.30,0:30:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你才"以为"你知道自己的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You think you know your own name?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.46,0:30:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是有多蠢啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How stupid are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.36,0:30:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 不要 哪儿也别去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mum, don't! Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.17,0:30:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也别打起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't start a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.01,0:30:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 不是这样的 他不是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mum! It's not like that, he's not. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.76,0:30:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回去 等我一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll be up in a minute hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.02,0:30:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那真的是一艘太空飞船吗 -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That was a real spaceship? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.27,0:30:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说全是谎话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So it's all a pack of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.73,0:30:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 它们是要入侵吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is it then? Are they invading?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.99,0:30:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多有趣的入侵方法 把全世界的人都惊到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Funny way to invade, putting the world on red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.16,0:30:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想法很好啊 它们究竟想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good point. So what they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.65,0:30:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,危机还在继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}As the crisis continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.11,0:30:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,政府部门表现得缺乏领导力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the Government shows remarkable lack of leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.95,0:30:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,整个国家充斥着各种流言\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}paranoia sweeps the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.03,0:30:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当局已经将三起公共袭击事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There've been at least three reports of public assaults
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.75,0:30:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,定性为疑似外星人所为\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}on people possibly identified as aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.89,0:30:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们把时间交给汤姆·海金森\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now back to Tom Hitchinson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.13,0:30:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还会有更多飞船来地球吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are there more ships to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.65,0:31:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,它们有什么目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And what's their intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.64,0:31:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当局希望 如果有谁了解任何相关信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The authorities are now asking, if anyone knows anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.11,0:31:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或发现过任何可疑迹象 请拨打该号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}if any previous sighting has been made, then call this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.71,0:31:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}外星人紧急热线
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.84,0:31:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要您的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.47,0:31:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}外星人紧急热线
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.44,0:31:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看到了一个真正的外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, I've seen one, I really have, an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.33,0:31:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她和他在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And she's with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.11,0:31:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我女儿和他在一起 我女儿处境危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My daughter, she's with him and she's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 她现在处境很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God, she's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.99,0:31:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我见到了一个外星人 我还知道他的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've seen an alien and I know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.39,0:31:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's called the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.45,0:31:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}博士
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.18,0:31:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个盒子 一个蓝色的盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a box, a blue box.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.79,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}蓝盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.19,0:31:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我女儿叫它塔迪斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She called it a TARDIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塔迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.17,0:31:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}红色警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.13,0:31:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}博士
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.88,0:31:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在下面干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So what you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.88,0:32:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇 -米奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ricky... - Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.76,0:32:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇 如果我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ricky, if I was to tell you what I was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.69,0:32:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么修理我酷炫的时间飞船控制系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}to the controls of my frankly magnificent timeship,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.91,0:32:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听懂哪怕一丁点吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}would you even begin to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.67,0:32:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,应该听不懂… -那就闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I suppose not. . .- Shut it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.68,0:32:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你交的这叫什么朋友 -他是想惹你发火\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Some friend you've got. - He's winding you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.25,0:32:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.76,0:32:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 -真的对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}OK. - I am, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.32,0:32:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都在找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Every day, I looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.38,0:32:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我走遍了大街小巷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}On every street corner, wherever I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.16,0:32:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,找那个蓝盒子 找了整整一年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Looking for a blue box. For a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.81,0:32:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说只过了几天而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's only been a few days for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.12,0:32:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不准 在盒子里很难分清时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I dunno, it's hard to tell inside this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.43,0:32:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可我发誓 我只离开了你短短几天而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but I swear, it's just a few days since I left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.53,0:32:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你还没来得及想我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not enough time to miss me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.14,0:32:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.50,0:33:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.29,0:33:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么在这12个月里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So, um, in 12 months. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.93,0:33:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你去和别人约会了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}have you been seeing anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.38,0:33:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.46,0:33:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好 -主要是大家都以为我杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}OK... - Mainly cos everyone thinks I murdered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.84,0:33:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.11,0:33:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So, now that you've come back. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.70,0:33:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你会留下来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}are you gonna stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.59,0:33:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.42,0:33:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雷达修好了 可以往前回看12个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Patched in the radar, looped it back 12 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.59,0:33:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以跟踪那艘飞船的飞行轨迹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}so it followed the flight of that spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.51,0:33:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看这儿 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here we go, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.46,0:33:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是那艘飞船飞向地球的轨迹 看到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's the spaceship on its way to Earth, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,除了… 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Except! Hold on. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.19,0:33:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗 那艘飞船在着陆前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}See? The space-ship did a slingshot
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.84,0:33:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,绕着地球飞行了一圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}round the Earth before it landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.86,0:33:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.55,0:33:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个飞船本身就是从地球上发射的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It came from Earth in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.06,0:33:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,发射升空 再落回地面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Went up and came back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.18,0:34:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不管那些外星生物究竟是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Whoever those aliens are,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.17,0:34:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它们可不是刚来到地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They haven't just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.10,0:34:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它们已经在地球上待了一阵子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They've been here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.20,0:34:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是 它们都做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Question is, what've they been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.27,0:34:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,效果如何 穿在身上紧不紧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What d'you think, how's the compression?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.73,0:34:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得腰部有点绷得慌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think I've got too much ballast round the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.87,0:34:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.46,0:34:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须先修理好气体交换系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We must fix the gas exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.41,0:34:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样太可笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's getting ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.26,0:34:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得这样更像人类了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know, seems human to me. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.71,0:34:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,最好处理掉他的人皮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Better get rid of his skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌 我还挺喜欢当奥利弗的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Shame, I quite enjoyed being Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.01,0:34:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他有一个老婆 一个情人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He had a wife, a mistress
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还和一个年轻的农民有一腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and a young farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.87,0:34:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 我都要忙死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}God, I was busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.40,0:34:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,开工了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.85,0:34:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在可以号令军队了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have an army to command!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.59,0:34:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点 我们还没到这一步呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Careful now. We're not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.44,0:34:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿斯奎斯将军 我们收到了高优先级的预警\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}General Asquith. Sir, we've had a priority alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.08,0:34:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是九号代码 确认是九号代码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it's Code Nine, confirmed Code Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.55,0:35:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好 很好 九号代码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right. Good. Code Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.00,0:35:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Which would mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.12,0:35:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急条例一旦生效\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In the event of emergency protocols being activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.13,0:35:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的软件会自动开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}our software automatically searches
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.95,0:35:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有通信渠道搜索关键词\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}all communications for keywords.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.93,0:35:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个关键词是 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And one of those words is "Doctor".
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.14,0:35:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们找到他了 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think we've found him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.85,0:35:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What sort of Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.20,0:35:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.98,0:35:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,显然他是某种处理外星事务的专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Evidently, he's some sort of expert in extraterrestrial affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.53,0:35:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,终极专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the ultimate expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.13,0:35:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要他 长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We need him, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.49,0:35:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就需要他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}we need him here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.89,0:35:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你这有几个频道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How many channels you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.97,0:35:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,基本收费频道都有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All the basic packages.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.81,0:35:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能看体育频道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You get Sports channels?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.57,0:35:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有 能看足球\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, I get the football.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.35,0:35:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 我认识这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold on. I know that lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.22,0:35:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来政府正在召集外星专家前来会商\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But likely that the government's bringing in alien-specialists,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.09,0:35:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们花费毕生心血\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}'those people who've devoted their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.22,0:35:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,研究外太空的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}to studying outer space.'
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.21,0:35:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,UNIT 联合国特别情报小组\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}UNIT, United Nations Intelligence Taskforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.20,0:35:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.18,0:35:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么认识他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How d'you know 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.70,0:35:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他为他们工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Cos he's worked for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.67,0:35:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别以为我12个月来光闲着了 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, yeah, don't think I sat on my backside for 12 months, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.99,0:35:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我研究了你的背景\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I read up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.60,0:36:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在网上和历史书里仔细找\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look deep enough on the Internet or in history books
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.85,0:36:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都能找到他的名字 所到之处死一堆人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}there's his name. Followed by a list of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.55,0:36:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 好样的 里奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's nice, good boy, Ricky
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.08,0:36:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你认识他们 为什么不去帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you know 'em, why not go and help?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.64,0:36:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认不出我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They wouldn't recognise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.50,0:36:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我变得跟以前不一样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've changed a lot since the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.91,0:36:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 现在世界正经历剧变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Besides, the world's on a knife-edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.58,0:36:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有外星人 还有假外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's aliens out there - and fake aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.36,0:36:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个外星人还是不要去搅和了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wanna keep this alien out of the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.65,0:36:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要伪装起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm going undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.68,0:36:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最好把塔迪斯藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'd better keep the Tardis out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.40,0:36:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇 你有车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ricky, you've got a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.21,0:36:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你来开车 -去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you can do some driving. - Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.41,0:36:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,交通恢复了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The roads are clearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们去看看那艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let's gonna have a look at that spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.93,0:36:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不许动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do not move!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.97,0:36:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.33,0:36:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.53,0:37:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把手举过头顶 你们被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Raise your hands above your heads! You are under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.12,0:37:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,带我去见你们的上司\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Take me to your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.30,0:37:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.86,0:37:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这车有点高级啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is a bit posh!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.44,0:37:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果知道被捕是这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If I'd known it would be like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.88,0:37:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好几年前我就要试试了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}being arrested, I would've done it years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.81,0:37:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是被捕 这是在护送我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're not being arrested, we're being escorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.56,0:37:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪儿 -你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where to? - Where d'you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.84,0:37:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,唐宁街\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Downing Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.30,0:37:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑 -我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're kidding! - I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.97,0:37:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,唐宁街十号 -就是那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}10 Downing Street? - That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.30,0:37:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.27,0:37:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去唐宁街十号了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm going to 10 Downing Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 -我不想这么说但是米奇是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How come? - I hate to say it, but Mickey was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.77,0:37:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年我拜访这颗星球太多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Over the years I've visited this planet, a lot of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.86,0:37:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经被…注意到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and I've been. . .noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.15,0:37:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now they need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.26,0:37:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就像新闻里说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Like it said on the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.36,0:37:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在召集具有外星知识的专家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they're gathering experts in alien knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.30,0:37:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人里谁是最权威的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who's the biggest expert of the lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.50,0:37:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1\bord0}{\an9}帕特里克·摩尔爵士 1923-2012 著名业余天文学家
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.50,0:37:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里克·摩尔 -除了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Patrick Moore. - Apart from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.32,0:37:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是喜欢这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't you just love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.99,0:37:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1\bord0}{\an9}劳合·乔治 1863-1945 曾任英国首相
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.99,0:37:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说 我以前跟劳合·乔治斗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ah, I'm telling you! Lloyd George,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.37,0:37:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,完全喝不过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}he used to drink me under the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.70,0:37:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在谁是首相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who's the Prime Minister now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.91,0:38:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道 我一年没在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How should I know? I missed a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.06,0:38:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.47,0:38:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她没事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So she's OK, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.87,0:38:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有惹什么麻烦吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's not in any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.30,0:38:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我能说的就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All I can say is that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,国家可能需要您女儿和她同伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}your daughter and her companion might be in a position
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.63,0:38:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,提供力所能及的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}to help the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.25,0:38:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要知道她是怎么跟那个人联系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We'll need to know how she made contact with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.51,0:38:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他是人类的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If he is a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.45,0:38:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你们可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right, off you go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.59,0:38:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要单独和泰勒夫人谈谈 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I need to talk with Mrs Tyler on my own, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.42,0:39:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哈丽特·琼斯 弗莱德尔北区议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Harriet Jones, MP Flydale North.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.96,0:39:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 请集中过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ladies and gentlemen, can we convene?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请尽快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Quick as we can please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这边 右手边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This way, on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.87,0:39:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒你们一下 请不要摘下身份卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can I remind you ID cards are to be worn at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.20,0:39:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是您的身份卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here's your ID card.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.79,0:39:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 您的同伴无权进入\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry, your companion doesn't have clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.79,0:39:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没有她我哪儿也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't go anywhere without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.93,0:39:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,九号代码是您 不是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're the Code Nine, not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.76,0:39:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, I'm sorry, er...Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.97,0:39:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是该叫您博士吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's the Doctor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.83,0:39:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要留在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She'll have to stay outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.13,0:39:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她得跟我在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's staying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.04,0:39:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,您看 连我都不能进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look, even I don't have clearance to go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.34,0:39:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让她进去 没得商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't let her in. That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.24,0:39:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 你去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's ok...You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.22,0:39:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 您是博士吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me, are you the Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.17,0:39:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗 -现在不行 我们很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are you sure? - Not now! We're busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.50,0:39:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能回家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}can't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要单独和他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I just need a word in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.46,0:39:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,您无权入内 不要纠缠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You haven't clearance. Leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.08,0:39:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫保安来送您出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll leave you with security.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.63,0:39:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 我来照看她 让我派点用处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's all right, I'll look after her. Let me be of some use.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.30,0:39:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我走走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Walk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.78,0:39:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just keep walking. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.69,0:39:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样 不要四处看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's right, don't look round.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哈丽特·琼斯 弗莱德尔北区议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Harriet Jones MP, Flydale North.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.63,0:40:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的这位朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This friend of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.00,0:40:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他确实是一位专家 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}he's an expert, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.63,0:40:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他了解 了解外星人的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He know... H-he knows about aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.13,0:40:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,您找他有什么事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why'd you wanna to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.45,0:40:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 请安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ladies and gentlemen, may I have your attention, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.85,0:40:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正如各位手中的摘要中所写\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}As you see from the summary in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.00,0:40:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘飞船的飞行员是一只类猪生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the ship had one porcine pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当然最有趣的部分发生在三天前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Of course the really interesting bit happened three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.80,0:40:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 归档在"其他"一栏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}See? Filed away under "Any other business".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.32,0:40:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,北海 一颗卫星探测到了一个信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The North Sea. A satellite detected a signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.15,0:41:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在水面下180米深的地方发出的辐射信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}a little blip of radiation at 100 fathoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.14,0:41:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎那里有什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Like there's something's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.94,0:41:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们正准备调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You were just about to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.33,0:41:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,结果发生了这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}next thing you know, this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.89,0:41:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太空飞船 猪 转移大众注意力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Spaceships, pigs, massive diversion
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.93,0:41:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.22,0:41:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把人变成了张皮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They turn the body into a suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.02,0:41:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的东西用人皮作伪装\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}a disguise, for the thing inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.64,0:41:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's all right, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.45,0:41:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那是外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's... it's, alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.63,0:41:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面肯定有什么高科技\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But they must have some serious technology behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.76,0:41:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们可以找出来 就可以加以利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If we could find it, we could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.38,0:41:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 这不是..\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God. Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.39,0:41:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哈丽特 天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Harriet, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.69,0:41:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是开玩笑 你不能到处晃悠\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is beyond a joke, you cannot just wander...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.01,0:41:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 这是首相大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God. That's the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.37,0:41:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是外星人假造了这起坠毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If aliens fake an alien crash
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.35,0:41:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,和外星人驾驶员 他们能有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and an alien pilot, what do they get?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.88,0:41:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.84,0:41:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就能得到我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是为了转移注意力 这是陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not a diversion, it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.71,0:41:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有人调皮捣蛋了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Has someone been naughty?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.97,0:42:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,里面比外面大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It was bigger on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.85,0:42:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我又不懂太空飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know! What do I know about spaceships?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.95,0:42:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是让我担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's what worries me. You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.85,0:42:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人是个麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}this man is classified as trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.21,0:42:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也就意味着 跟他牵扯上的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}which means that anyone associated with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.26,0:42:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也是麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}is trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的工作就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And that's my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.07,0:42:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,解决麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}eliminating trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.04,0:42:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.43,0:42:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他今天下午离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He left this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.41,0:42:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 首相离开了唐宁街\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I mean, the Prime Minister left Downing Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.72,0:42:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他被开车送走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}he was driven away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.38,0:42:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.40,0:42:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.71,0:42:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是冲我们来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.05,0:42:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,外星专家 唯一知道如何与他们战斗的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Alien experts, the only people who know how to fight them
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.14,0:42:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,被聚集在一处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}gathered together in one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.72,0:43:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我拯救世界的时候您能别放屁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me. D'you mind not farting while I'm saving the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.79,0:43:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你更喜欢不出声但却致命的那种吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Would you rather silent but deadly?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.97,0:44:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是斯利辛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We are the Slitheen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.23,0:45:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你们始终佩戴着身份证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank you all for wearing your ID. Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.72,0:45:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮助我们辨识尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They'll help to identify the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.00,0:45:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,0)\pos(171.856,183.273)}{\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.47,0:45:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我们刚看到了新世界的黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yesterday saw the start of a brave new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.92,0:45:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也许我们将目睹新世界的终结\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Today might see it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.27,0:45:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi. If you want aliens, you've got 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.78,0:45:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就在唐宁街里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're inside Downing Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.02,0:45:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,地球正式开战\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Planet Earth is at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.81,0:46:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Everybody run!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.19,0:46:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,斯利辛到底是谁 -外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who exactly are Slitheen? - They're aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.91,0:46:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我能拯救世界却要失去你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I could save the world but lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
